:::Nemesis looked coolly at the wildly slashing bot, he stepped out of the 
way of the slashes and spoke:::

Nemesis; "You think that a few months of practice will defeat me? i have 
spent my entire life honing my power to an art"

:::he held up his hand and the world seemed to rumble a globe of black light 
appeared in his hand and shot at Vulois. Then, before they hit him they 
disappeared. Nemesis Jumped in the air and folded his legs, he began to 
meditate large rocks all around him rose in the air and then burst into 
flames. The ashes of the rock swirled around Nemesis it disappeared nemesis 
set himself down and gathered energy. the energy flamed around him and then 
flew towards Vulois:::

:::Child was weak, he had used so much energy. He mustered up some strength 
and sent it all to Vulois. he felt the rest of his energy flow into vulois. 
Child whispered:::

Child; "Defeat him vulois, ge rid of him.................."

:::Child went into stasis lock:::
